name: Black Curls Neckpiece
description:
Black Curls Neckpiece is made from recycled innertubes from bicycle tires, horn beads, coiled copper and silver metal washers. It is on memory wire, with a magnetic clasp. 

Born out of a new series for a recycled jewelry exhibition and a working bicycle repair shop at the art center where I spend my days. Patchwork Central offer free arts programs to neighborhood kids in Evansville's inner city area. 20% of the price is this neck piece will go to arts programming. See www.patchwork.org for more info.

Jewelry with a social conscience! What more could you ask for?

description:
